   Beginner's list: http://groups.yahoo.com/group/ocaml_beginners
   Bug reports: http://caml.inria.fr/bin/caml-bugs

This address is invalid now.

I believe a serious website should not change all URL's at every
reorganisation. If URL's change, the webserver should relocate
the old ones such that old bookmarks continue to work.

